cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CE, cs.SI, cs.HC 

The paper proposes a methodology that involves Machine Learning (ML) and Bayesian Optimization (BO) to suggest cooking recipes. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science). Additionally, the paper involves simulations and optimization, which could fit into cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) sub-categories, respectively.
